{
  "texts": [
    "This 73% success rate substantially improves over the ∼50% success rate for HTS 21, 67.",
    "On average, we screened 85 compounds per project and discovered 4.6 active hits, with an average hit rate of 5.5%.",
    "For the subset of targets where we found any hits, the average was 6.4 hits per project.",
    "Thus, we achieved an average hit rate of 7.6%, which again compares favorably with typical HTS hit rates.",
    "See Supplementary Material S1 for all assay definitions and conditions."
  ]
}